UID:puppettype@cfgmgmtcamp.eu
SUMMARY:Puppet's Type & Provider Module Extraction Saga
ORGANIZER:Jorie Tappa
CATEGORIES:talk
DTSTAMP:20181231T000000Z
TZID:Europe-Brussels
DTSTART:20190204T140000
DTEND:20190204T145500
DESCRIPTION:"In Puppet 6, we removed several core types and providers into modules, and published most of those onto the Puppet Forge.  This talk covers the history and motivation behind removing them, hurdles we faced, module authorship with PDK, setting up CI pipelines,and the behind the scenes view of how the extracted modules are repackaged back into Puppet agent.  "
